name: market for sawlog and veneer log, eucalyptus ssp., measured as solid wood under bark | sawlog and veneer log, eucalyptus ssp., measured as solid wood under bark | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/22679/documentation

This is a market activity. Each market represents the consumption mix of a product in a given geography, connecting suppliers with consumers of the same product in the same geographical area. Markets group the producers and also the imports of the product (if relevant) within the same geographical area. They also account for transport to the consumer and for the losses during that process, when relevant.;This is the market for  'sawlog and veneer log, eucalyptus ssp., measured as solid wood under bark', in the geography of Thailand.;Transport from producers to consumers of this product in the geography covered by the market is included.;The product 'sawlog and veneer log, eucalyptus (Eucalyptus camaldulensis), measured as solid wood under bark' represents tropical roundwood from the hardwood species Eucalyptus camaldulensis. The amount is expressed as solid wood including bark. Production takes place in the forest. In the ecoinvent database, eucalyptus sawlog and veneer log is used for the production of eucalyptus sulfate pulp production, particle board production, and for the production of eucalyptus poles used for fencing. 

Activity starts with the product ready for shipment.

Activity ends with the reception of the product at the consuming entity. Average transportation requirements from producer to consuming entity are covered.
